column2:
For example, if using terminal:
curl --request POST \
  --url https://preview.api.climatiq.io/travel/v1-preview1/spend \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "spend_type": "air",
    "money": 100,
    "money_unit": "gbp",
    "spend_location": {
        "locode": "GB-LON"
    },
    "spend_year": 2018
}'
